delhi in a day is a 2013 indian drama film written and directed by prashant nair and produced by prashant nair . the film stars manoj bajpayee , prashant narayanan , mohan agashe and mohan agashe in the lead roles . the film was produced by prashant nair and prashant nair . delhi in a day was the first indian film to be produced by prashant nair and prashant nair . delhi in a day was screened at the 2013 delhi international film festival .